msgid "0:葉月メガネ有り"
msgstr "0:葉月メガネ有り"

msgid "100:葉月メガネ無し"
msgstr "100:葉月メガネ無し"

msgid "200:完全なる白の中――[%p]"
msgstr "200:The world around me was perfectly white.[%p]"

msgid "300:僕は、横たわっている。[%p]"
msgstr "300:I was lying down.[%p]"

msgid "400:ふわふわとした浮遊感。でも自分が浮いているのかどうか分からない。上下左右の感覚すらない。[%p]"
msgstr "400:It felt like I was floating. But I couldn't tell if I was. I couldn't tell which way was up, and which way was down.[%p]"

msgid "500:静寂が耳にうるさい。[linebreak]まるで頭の中で何百匹っていうスズムシが一斉に鳴いてるみたいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "500:The silence was loud in my ears. It was like hundreds of crickets were chirping in my head.[%p]"

msgid "600:ここが死後の世界だって言われても、僕はなんら疑うことをしないだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "600:If somebody had told me this was the afterlife, I wouldn't have doubted it for a second.[%p]"

msgid "700:それくらい、ここは、[%p]"
msgstr "700:The place was just so...[%p]"

msgid "800:単調で、[%p]"
msgstr "800:Monotone.[%p]"

msgid "900:簡素で、[%p]"
msgstr "900:Empty.[%p]"

msgid "1000:静謐で、[%p]"
msgstr "1000:Silent.[%p]"

msgid "1100:規則的で、[%p]"
msgstr "1100:Orderly.[%p]"

msgid "1200:整然としていて、[%p]"
msgstr "1200:Organized.[%p]"

msgid "1300:なにもなく、[%p]"
msgstr "1300:Vacant.[%p]"

msgid "1400:安らかだ。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:And peaceful.[%p]"

msgid "1500:悟りを開いた釈迦の脳内はこんなだったかもしれない。[linebreak]僕の脳内とは、大違いだ。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:This must've been what the Buddha's brain was like after he achieved enlightenment. It wasn't like my brain at all.[%p]"

msgid "1600:いつまでもここにいたい。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:I wanted to stay here forever.[%p]"

msgid "1700:現実の煩わしさとか、辛さとか、苦しさとか、虚しさとか。そういうものを味わいたくない――[%p]"
msgstr "1700:All the crap I had to put up with in the real world, the pain, the suffering, the emptiness... I didn't want to deal with any of it.[%p]"

msgid "1800:そう思っていた矢先に、それまで無音だったこの白い世界に、雑音が飛び込んでくる。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:And then, a noise disrupted the silent white world.[%p]"

msgid "1900:それはドアを開ける音。[linebreak]そして誰かの足音。[linebreak]近づいてくる――[%p]"
msgstr "1900:It was the sound of a door opening, and the sound of somebody's footsteps. They were coming closer.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]七海[line]「おにぃ、来たよー」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]七海[line]Brother, I came to see you![%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]七海[line]「んしょ、んしょ……」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]七海[line]Let's see... Here it is...[%p]"

msgid "2200:[name]七海[line]「おにぃおにぃ。今日ね、ナナね、いいもの持ってきたんだよー」[%p]"
msgstr "2200:[name]七海[line]Brother, Brother! I brought you something![%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]七海[line]「はい、これ。プレゼント！」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]七海[line]Look! A present![%p]"

msgid "2400:[name]七海[line]「手編みの帽子なんだよ。すごいでしょ？\u3000すごいでしょー？」[%p]"
msgstr "2400:[name]七海[line]It's a hand-knit cap. It's great, isn't it? Isn't it?[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]七海[line]「もう冬だしね、ナナね、帽子好きだから、編んだの！」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]七海[line]It's winter, and I like caps, so I knitted one for you![%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]七海[line]「使ってね！」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]七海[line]Use it, okay?[%p]"

msgid "2700:[name]七海[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "2700:[name]七海[line]...[%p]"

msgid "2800:[name]七海[line]「おにぃ！\u3000無視しないでよー！」[%p]"
msgstr "2800:[name]七海[line]Brother! Don't ignore me![%p]"

msgid "2900:[name]七海[line]「あー！\u3000ごはん、残してるじゃん！\u3000せっかくのカレーなのに」[%p]"
msgstr "2900:[name]七海[line]Hey! You didn't finish your meal! And it's curry today, too![%p]"

msgid "3000:[name]七海[line]「ちゃんと食べないとダメなんだよー」[%p]"
msgstr "3000:[name]七海[line]You need to eat![%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]七海[line]「ねーねー、病院のごはんっておいしくないって、ホント？」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]七海[line]Hey, is it true that hospital food isn't very good?[%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]七海[line]「でも食べないとダメー」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]七海[line]But you need to eat![%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]七海[line]「起きろー、おにぃ！\u3000食べずに寝たら[linebreak]夜になっておなかすいちゃうんだからー！」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]七海[line]Get up, Brother! If you go to sleep without eating, you'll get hungry in the middle of the night![%p]"

msgid "3400:誰かの手が、僕の背中に回される。[linebreak]そして無理矢理、身体を起こされる。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:Somebody's hand came around to my back. They pushed me and sat me up.[%p]"

msgid "3500:僕はそこで初めて、[linebreak]自分が目を閉じていたことに気付く。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:It was only then... That I realized my eyes were closed.[%p]"

msgid "3600:目を開くと、そこに小さな女の子がいた。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:I opened them and there was a small girl there.[%p]"

msgid "3700:こいつは七海だ。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:It was Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "3800:僕の妹。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:My little sister.[%p]"

msgid "3900:でもやけに小さい。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:But she was so small.[%p]"

msgid "4000:昔の七海だ。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:It was Nanami as she'd looked several years ago.[%p]"

msgid "4100:どれぐらい前だろう。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:How many years, though?[%p]"

msgid "4200:少なくとも小学生の頃なのは確かだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:She had to be in elementary school, at least.[%p]"

msgid "4300:[name]七海[line]「はい、あーんして」[%p]"
msgstr "4300:[name]七海[line]Okay, say, “Aah!”[%p]"

msgid "4400:幼い七海が、プラスチック製のスプーンにカレーをすくい、差し出してくる。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:The young Nanami scooped up curry with a plastic spoon and offered it to me.[%p]"

msgid "4500:僕は――[linebreak]スプーンを持つ七海の手をはたき、[%p]"
msgstr "4500:And I... I knocked her hand away.[%p]"

msgid "4600:さらになにを思ったか、[linebreak]カレーライスが載せられたトレーを、腕で振り払うようにして床にぶちまけた。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:And for some reason, I swept the tray with the curry rice onto the floor with my arm.[%p]"

msgid "4700:[name]七海[line]「…………あ」[%p]"
msgstr "4700:[name]七海[line]Oh...[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]七海[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]七海[line]...[%p]"

msgid "4900:[name]七海[line]「はあ」[%p]"
msgstr "4900:[name]七海[line]Sigh...[%p]"

msgid "5000:[name]七海[line]「おにぃ、お行儀悪いんだー。お母さんに言いつけてやるぞー」[%p]"
msgstr "5000:[name]七海[line]Brother, you've got such bad table manners. I'll tell Mommy on you.[%p]"

msgid "5100:七海は床にしゃがみこむと、ぶちまけられたトレーを拾い、さらに部屋の隅にある洗面台から雑巾を持ってきて、掃除を始める。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:Nanami crouched down and picked up the tray. Next, she brought a washcloth over from the sink in the corner of the room and began to clean up its splattered contents.[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]七海[line]「ホント、世話が焼けるなあ」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]七海[line]You really are a handful.[%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]七海[line]「ナナがいないとなーんにもできないんだから」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]七海[line]You can't do anything without me, you know.[%p]"

msgid "5400:――もう、やめてよ。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:Just leave me alone.[%p]"

msgid "5500:僕は両手で顔を覆い、ゆっくりと目を閉じた。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:I covered my face with my hands and slowly closed my eyes.[%p]"

msgid "5600:[name]梨深[line]「ごめんね、あなたを、守ってあげられなくて」[%p]"
msgstr "5600:[name]梨深[line]I'm sorry I couldn't protect you.[%p]"

msgid "5700:ゆっくりと目を開くと、白い天井が見えた。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:I slowly opened my eyes, and saw a white ceiling.[%p]"

msgid "5800:白が、まぶしい。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:The white was dazzlingly bright.[%p]"

msgid "5900:何度かまぶたをまたたかせる。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:I blinked a few times.[%p]"

msgid "6000:指先を動かしてみる。[linebreak]手を顔の上に掲げてみる。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:I tried moving my fingers. I brought my hand up to my face.[%p]"

msgid "6100:手のひらが影を作ってくれた。[linebreak]それでようやく、まぶしさから解放された。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:My hand made a shadow, blocking the light. Only then was I free from the brightness.[%p]"

msgid "6200:夢を見ていた。七海の夢だ。[linebreak]七海は昔から、しっかり者だった。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:I'd been dreaming. It was a dream about Nanami. Nanami had always been such a little grown-up.[%p]"

msgid "6300:小学生の頃、バス事故で僕が誰とも口を利かなくなったことで、七海はますますその傾向を強めた。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:That tendency of hers had only gotten more pronounced when I'd stopped talking to everybody after the bus accident.[%p]"

msgid "6400:ただ過保護なだけになった両親と違い、口では僕に厳しくしながらあれこれと世話をしてくれたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:My parents just became overprotective, but whatever mean things Nanami might say, she would always try and take care of me.[%p]"

msgid "6500:でも、あの夢は――[%p]"
msgstr "6500:But that dream...[%p]"

msgid "6600:僕って入院したことなんてあったっけ？[linebreak]通院はしてたけど……。[linebreak]まあ、夢だからその程度の違いを真面目に考えるのは無意味か。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:Had I ever stayed at a hospital like that? I'd been going to one, but never stayed there... right? Well, there was no point in trying to read too much into a dream.[%p]"

msgid "6700:僕はベッドに横たわっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:I was lying down on a bed.[%p]"

msgid "6800:白いパイプベッドだ。[linebreak]シーツは白。枕は白。リノリウムの床は白。壁紙も白。[linebreak]天上の蛍光灯も白。窓を覆っているカーテンも白。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:It was a simple white bed. The sheets were white. The pillows were white. The linoleum floor was white. The wallpaper was white, too. Even the fluorescent lights on the ceiling were white. The curtains on the windows were white.[%p]"

msgid "6900:ベッドの横にある小さな棚も白。[linebreak]その上に置かれた陶器の水差しも白。紙コップも白。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:The tiny shelf next to the bed was white. The porcelain pitcher on it was white. The paper cups were white.[%p]"

msgid "7000:だんだんうんざりしてきた。[linebreak]思い切って上半身を起こしてみる。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:I was starting to get sick of all the white. I tried forcing myself to sit up.[%p]"

msgid "7100:一瞬だけ、腰のあたりに痺れるような痛みが走った。でもすぐに治まる。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:For a single instant, I felt a numbing pain around my lower back, but it quickly vanished.[%p]"

msgid "7200:部屋はけっこう広い。少なくとも僕のベースの２倍はある。でもとにかく殺風景だった。病室なのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:The room was pretty big. Twice the size of the Base, at least. But it was empty. It might've been a hospital room.[%p]"

msgid "7300:ベッドのすぐ下に、緑色のスリッパが一足並べてあった。[linebreak]白以外の色を見つけて、ホッとする。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:I could see a single pair of green slippers just under the bed. I felt relieved to find something that wasn't white.[%p]"

msgid "7400:身体もちゃんと動くし、僕は死んだわけじゃないらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "7400:I was moving, and I wasn't dead, from the look of it.[%p]"

msgid "7500:のどが渇いていた。[linebreak]コーラが飲みたい。炭酸の利いた冷たいコーラを。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:My throat was dry. I wanted a soda. A cold, fizzy soda.[%p]"

msgid "7600:でもこの真っ白な部屋にそんなものがあるわけもなく、仕方なく水差しから直接水を口に注いだ。[%p]"
msgstr "7600:But of course, there was nothing like that in this pure white room. I ended up pouring water from the pitcher directly into my mouth.[%p]"

msgid "7700:少し生ぬるかったけど、それでものどを潤すにはじゅうぶんだった。[%p]"
msgstr "7700:It was a little warm, but enough to slake my thirst.[%p]"

msgid "7800:水を飲み終えて一息ついていると、ドアが開いて白衣の看護師さんが入ってきた。[linebreak]それで、やっぱりここが病院だって分かった。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:After I finished drinking my water and taking a moment to catch my breath, the door opened and a white-clad nurse came in. So this place was a hospital after all, then.[%p]"

msgid "7900:相手は僕を見るなり、少しだけ目を丸くする。どうやらまだ寝てると思ってたらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:She seemed a little surprised as she looked at me. She'd thought I was still asleep, it seemed.[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]看護師[line]「あら……」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]看護師[line]Oh, my...[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]看護師[line]「西條さん、目が覚めたんですね」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]看護師[line]Nishijo, you're awake.[%p]"

msgid "8200:すぐに優しい笑みを向けてきた。[linebreak]看護師の鑑だね。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:She smiled gently at me. What a great nurse she was.[%p]"

msgid "8300:っていうかこの人、どこかで見たことあるような……。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:Wait... I felt like I'd seen her somewhere before.[%p]"

msgid "8400:あ、そうか。前に高科先生に診てもらったときに、病院にいたおねいさんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:Oh, now I remember... I'd met her when I'd gone to see Dr. Takashina.[%p]"

msgid "8500:名前はなんて言ったっけ……。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:What was her name again?[%p]"

msgid "8600:思い出せないので、胸元のネームプレートをチラリと盗み見た。[linebreak]“葉月”と書かれてあった。[%p]"
msgstr "8600:I couldn't remember, so I glanced at the name tag on her chest. “Hazuki,” it read.[%p]"

msgid "8700:そうそう、葉月さん。[%p]"
msgstr "8700:Right, right. Hazuki.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]葉月[line]「お身体の調子はどうですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]葉月[line]How are you feeling?[%p]"

msgid "8900:葉月さんは自然な仕草で、体温計を僕に差し出してきた。なんとなく受け取ってしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "8900:She offered me a thermometer. I took it, without really thinking about what was going on.[%p]"

msgid "9000:[name]葉月[line]「体温を測ってくださいね」[%p]"
msgstr "9000:[name]葉月[line]Take your temperature for me, okay?[%p]"

msgid "9100:そんなに優しく言われたら、素直に従うしかなくなっちゃうよね……。頭の中は疑問符だらけだったけど、とりあえず体温計を腋に挟んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:I couldn't say no if she was going to be this nice. My head was overflowing with doubts, but I put the thermometer under my arm anyway.[%p]"

msgid "9200:直後に、記憶が僕の頭の中で弾けた。[linebreak]思い出す。[linebreak]あの出来事を。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:Then the memories burst inside my head. I remembered... Remembered what had happened before.[%p]"

msgid "9300:あのとき――[%p]"
msgstr "9300:Up on the roof...[%p]"

msgid "9400:七海を助けるのを、あきらめた僕は。[linebreak]車椅子の『将軍』につかみかかった。[%p]"
msgstr "9400:After I'd given up on saving Nanami, I'd charged Shogun in his wheelchair.[%p]"

msgid "9500:でも手応えはなくて、もつれるように倒れた僕が抱えていたのは、ダーススパイダーのヘルメットだった。[%p]"
msgstr "9500:But there was nobody there. I'd fallen over and found myself holding a Darth Spider helmet.[%p]"

msgid "9600:ダーススパイダー伯爵。映画『スパークウォーズ』に登場する悪の代名詞。黒ずくめの姿は日本でも有名だ。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Count Darth Spider was a famous villain from the movie Spark Wars. His all-black silhouette was famous even in Japan.[%p]"

msgid "9700:でも、まさか『将軍』がダーススパイダーのコスプレをしていたとは思いも寄らなくて、僕は怒りも吹き飛んでしまい、ただただ困惑した。[%p]"
msgstr "9700:I'd never expected in a million years to find that Shogun was wearing a Darth Spider cosplay. All my anger melted away, replaced by confusion.[%p]"

msgid "9800:立ち上がって、車椅子を見た。[linebreak]……誰も座っていなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "9800:I stood up and looked at the wheelchair. Nobody was in it.[%p]"

msgid "9900:黒いフードが背もたれ部分にかけられていた。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:There was a black hooded robe draped over the back of the chair.[%p]"

msgid "10000:それもまた、ダーススパイダーの衣装だった。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:It was part of Darth Spider's costume, too.[%p]"

msgid "10100:さらに周囲を見回してみたけど、誰もいなかった。[linebreak]あの真っ暗な屋上にいたのは、僕だけだったんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:I looked around to see if anyone else was there, but there wasn't. I was the only person on the dark roof.[%p]"

msgid "10200:そこへ、報道陣が一斉に駆け込んできた。[%p]"
msgstr "10200:Then the media came rushing in.[%p]"

msgid "10300:彼らは僕を隙間なく取り囲み、マイクと、カメラと、照明を向けてきた。[linebreak]その数は１０本どころじゃ済まなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:They surrounded me with microphones, cameras, and lighting. There was nowhere to turn. I didn't count how many people were there, but at least a dozen.[%p]"

msgid "10400:そのあまりの勢いに、僕は恐怖すら覚えた。[linebreak]逃げ出したかったけど、一歩も動けなかった。[linebreak]もみくちゃだった。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:The sheer intensity of them all terrified me. I wanted to run, but I couldn't move an inch. They were crushing me.[%p]"

msgid "10500:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]「西條くん！\u3000西條くん！\u3000透視はどうなっちゃったのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "10500:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]Nishijo! Nishijo! What did your psychic powers tell you?[%p]"

msgid "10600:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]「結局、ニュージェネの犯人は誰なのか分からないということですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "10600:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]Does this mean you failed to find out who's behind the NewGen murders?[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]「そのダーススパイダーのヘルメットは[linebreak]なにか超能力と関係あるのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]Does that Darth Spider helmet have something to do with your powers?[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]芸能レポーターＣ[line]「西條さん！\u3000答えてくれませんかぁ？\u3000これで終わりなんて言うなら、電波ジャックですよ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]芸能レポーターＣ[line]Nishijo! Would you please answer us? If this is the end of the show, you just hijacked the airwaves for nothing![%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]「結局なにがしたかったんです？\u3000ニュージェネに便乗した売名行為ですか？\u3000不謹慎だと思わないんですか！？」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]What was the point of all this? Are you trying to use the NewGen murders to get famous? Don't you think that's a little inappropriate?[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]「ユーリ・ブライトマンさんとは最近話したかな？\u3000どんなことを話した？」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]Have you talked to Yuri Brightman lately? What did you talk about?[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]芸能レポーターＣ[line]「地震とニュージェネについてなにか関係あると思いますかぁ？」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]芸能レポーターＣ[line]Do you think there's a connection between the earthquake and NewGen?[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]「その手に持っている美少女フィギュアは、なんらかの儀式的なアイテムと考えていいんですか？」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]Is that anime figurine you're holding in your hands for some kind of ritual?[%p]"

msgid "11300:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]「このような行動を取ったことには、アニメやゲームの影響はあったのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "11300:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]Did anime or video games make you do this?[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]芸能レポーターＣ[line]「西條さん！」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]芸能レポーターＣ[line]Nishijo![%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]「西條さん！」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]芸能レポーターＢ[line]Nishijo![%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]「西條くん！」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]芸能レポーターＡ[line]Nishijo![%p]"

msgid "11700:向けられる照明が、すごく熱い。[%p]"
msgstr "11700:The lights were so bright.[%p]"

msgid "11800:まるで真夏の太陽の下で肌を焼かれているみたいに感じる。殺到するマスコミの人いきれもあって、頭がボーッとしてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:It felt like my flesh was burning under a midsummer sun. There were so many people around me that the heat of their bodies was making my head feel woozy.[%p]"

msgid "11900:グルグルと、視界が回っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:My vision was spinning.[%p]"

msgid "12000:追い込まれて。[linebreak]パニックになって。[linebreak]息が苦しくて。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I was pushed into a corner, panicking. I couldn't breathe.[%p]"

msgid "12100:頭を抱えた。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:I put my hands to my head.[%p]"

msgid "12200:なにも見えない。なにも見たくない。[linebreak]なにも聞こえない。なにも聞きたくない。[linebreak]なにも感じない。なにも感じたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:I couldn't see a thing. I didn't want to see a thing. I couldn't hear a thing. I didn't want to hear anything. I couldn't feel a thing. I didn't want to feel a thing.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]拓巳[line]「やめ……て……」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]拓巳[line]Stop...[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]拓巳[line]「やめてくれぇぇっ！！」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]拓巳[line]Stop it![%p]"

msgid "12500:叫ぶと同時に、意識が、ショートしたように、ブツンと途切れた――[%p]"
msgstr "12500:And as I screamed, my mind went blank, like it had short circuited.[%p]"

msgid "12600:そうだ……。[linebreak]僕は意識を失って――[%p]"
msgstr "12600:That's right. I passed out.[%p]"

msgid "12700:それで……？[linebreak]それから、どうなって、この病院に来たんだっけ。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:And then... How'd I end up here after that?[%p]"

msgid "12800:覚えてない。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:I couldn't remember.[%p]"

msgid "12900:少なくとも自分の足でここに来たとは思えない。ということは救急車で運ばれたのかも。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:If nothing else, I was sure I hadn't walked here on my own. Maybe I'd been brought here by an ambulance?[%p]"

msgid "13000:葉月さんは持っていたクリップボードに、なにやら書き込んでいる。そこに紙でも挟んであるんだろう。書いている内容は、僕の容体についてかな……？[%p]"
msgstr "13000:Hazuki was writing something on the clipboard in her hand. There must have been some kind of paper stuck on it. Was she writing down my symptoms?[%p]"

msgid "13100:彼女の手首に巻いてある飾り気のない腕時計から、今が何時なのか確認した。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:I was able to check the time from the simple, nondescript wristwatch on her arm.[%p]"

msgid "13200:午前６時過ぎ。[linebreak]どうやらだいぶ眠ってたらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "13200:It was just past six in the morning. I'd been out for a long time, from the look of it.[%p]"

msgid "13300:それにしてもどうしてこの病院に運ばれたんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:But why this hospital, though?[%p]"

msgid "13400:葉月さんがいるっていうことは、僕の行きつけの病院だよね、ここって。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:If Hazuki was here, that meant it was the one I usually went to.[%p]"

msgid "13500:確かに総合病院であるここに僕が運ばれても、おかしくはないんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:This place was a big general hospital. I could see somebody deciding to bring me here.[%p]"

msgid "13600:でもなんだかしっくり来ない。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:But something still didn't seem right.[%p]"

msgid "13700:“どうして葉月さんが僕の様子を見に来るのか”っていうのが引っかかる。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:I wasn't sure why Hazuki would be the one assigned to me.[%p]"

msgid "13800:だって葉月さんは、精神科の看護師さんなんだぞ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13800:She worked in the psychiatric ward, right?[%p]"

msgid "13900:その葉月さんが様子を見に来たっていうことは、この病室も精神科の患者が使う部屋なんじゃないの？[%p]"
msgstr "13900:If she was here, did that mean this room was usually used by mental patients?[%p]"

